programme.title: Born To Raise Hell

Och nar en medlem i teamet blir mordad har Axel bara en tanke i huvudet: Hamnd!

programme.title: Miami Supercops
programme.desc: Har kommer annu en actionspackad komedi från den dynamiska duon Hill och Spencer. I "Miami Supercops" ser vi våra hjaltar jaga både brottslingar och 20 miljoner dollar som stals vid ett rån for ett par år sedan. Vi får uppleva mord, forodelse och totalt kaos under deras jakt på bytet och rånarna - och naturligtvis får de hjalp av två snygga tjejer!

programme.title: Final Shot
programme.desc: Lonnmordaren Frank har lagt sitt tidigare arbete på hyllan och forsoker leva ett till synes vanligt liv tillsammans med flickvannen och hans dotter. En dag kommer en okand maffia boss forbi for att få Franks hjalp att ha ihjal den som tagit livet av hans unga dotter. For att inte dra in sin egen familj i eventuella komplikationer måste Frank fatta ett beslut om att gora stoten åt bossen eller få ro med sin egen sjal?

programme.title: Bulletproof Monk
programme.desc: The Monk ar en zen-cool martial arts-mastare vars uppgift har varit att beskydda en maktig antik skrift, en mystisk artefakt som bar nyckeln till obegransad makt. Nu har The Monk inlett sitt sokande efter skriftens naste vaktare, och uppdraget for honom till USA.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Den italienska westernstjarnan Bud Spencer (hans riktiga namn ar Carlo Pedersoli) spelar en godhjartad men jarnnavad bananodlare som bor i en liten djungelby. Ett stort bananforetag vill exploatera byn, och nar Joe satter sig på tvaren bestammer sig foretagsledaren – en gangster – att satta dit honom. Resultatet ar ett komiskt aventyr med många energiska slagsmål.

programme.title: Wild Target
programme.desc: En klumpig yrkesmordare blir foralskad i sitt offer och måste skydda henne från både sin egen organisation och polisen.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: Skurkar och banditer
programme.desc: Tony Roma (Tomas Milian) ar alla tiders halaste gigolo, en sol-och-vårare och skojare specialiserad på att knycka formogna hemmafruars diamanter. Till slut kopplas den hemliga polisen Parker (Bud Spencer) in for att ta fast den lille skojaren. Parker vill helst åka på semester med sin stora familj. Istallet tvingas han nu skydda Tony sedan denne blivit vittne till ett maffiamord. Sjalvklart haglar råsoparna och smockorna nar Parker tar sig an maffiaganget och kastar skurkarna rakt igenom dorrar och vaggar.

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Jumper
programme.desc: Av regissoren till The Bourne Identity kommer annu en extrem adrenalinchock som tanjer på fantasins begransningar… David Rice ar en ung man utan granser – en “jumper” – fodd med den markliga formågan att kunna teleportera sig sjalv vart som helst på jorden inom ett ogonblick. Nar David upptacker att det finns fler som honom sjalv kastas han plotsligt in mitt i ett forntida krig. Han jagas av en blodtorstig skara fanatiker, fast beslutna att utrota alla jumpers. Nu måste David anvanda sin mycket speciella gåva smart for att ha en chans att overleva…

programme.title: Immortals
programme.desc: Efter att de grekiska krigarna till slut vunnit over Titanerna, dyker ett nytt hot upp mot dem. Med enorm kraft, deklarerar Kung Hyperon krig mot hela manskligheten. Med sin blodtorstiga och vansinniga arme soker Hyperion genom Grekland efter den legendariske Epirus båge, ett vapen med obeskrivlig kraft, som smidits i himlen av sjalvaste Ares sjalv. Om vapnet hamnar i kungens ago, kan det forgora hela manskligheten, till och med forinta gudarna. Men de forntida lagarna forbjuder gudarna att ingripa i manskliga konflikter och gudarna forblir maktlosa mot Hyperion och hans arme.

programme.title: Blood And Bone
programme.desc: Isaiah Bone (Michael Jai White) ar en skicklig mastare i kampsport. Efter fem år bakom galler skall han nu ut i verkligheten och borja ett nytt liv. Han anlander till Los Angeles dar ingen vet vem han ar och dar overraskar han alla genom att slåss som en varldsmastare. På gatorna i LA ar det gangsterkungen James som styr och Bone tar sig snart an utmaningen att forsoka storta honom. Men Bone doljer en mork hemlighet och han ar dessutom ute efter hamnd. Bone upptacker snart att han måste slåss for sitt liv. Allt står på spel! EN VISUELLT BLÄNDANDE ACTIONFILM MED MICHAEL JAI WHITE (’Spawn’), JULIAN SANDS (’24 timmar’) OCH NONA GAYE (’Matrix Reloaded’).

programme.title: Texas Killing Fields
programme.desc: Mellan 1983 och 1991 hittas fyra kvinnokroppar på samma plats i en stad i Texas. The Fields ar den sanna historien om en mans trettioåriga kamp for att losa mordgåtan, i det forgiftade oljelandskapet som kallas for Killing Fields.

programme.title: A Good Man
programme.desc: Efter att en lysande karriar inom en militar specialstyrka slutar i katastrof, drar sig Alexander (Seagal) undan rampljuset och forsoker leva ett lugnt liv som hantverkare i ett lagenhetskomplex i Rumanien.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Udda eller jamt
programme.desc: Polisen har misslyckats med att krossa ligan som svarar for den illegala spelverksamheten i Florida. Marinofficeren Johnny Firpo (Terence Hill) tar over uppdraget och raknar med hjalp av ex-spelaren Charlie Firpo (Bud Spencer). Det udda paret visar sig vara halvbroder, men Charlie vill andå inte hjalpa Johnny. Inte forran denne ljuger ihop en historia om att deras far ar blind och måste genomgå en dyr operation. Charlie inser att han måste tjana ihop till operationen genom ett antal poker- och spelvinster. Som vanligt får paret också många tillfallen att utnyttja sina stenhårda navar!

programme.title: Legal Action
programme.desc: Stjarnadvokaten Casey McKay lockas till en liten stad av sin exfru for att forsvara hennes bror som står åtalad for att ha mordat en distriktsåklagare. Casey blottlagger en konspirationsharva som staller honom oga mot oga med mr Gates, stadens allra mest korrupte markexploator. En f.d. marinsoldat hjalper Casey i konflikten nar det står klart att han behover mer an sitt juridiska kunnande for att hålla sig vid liv och radda sin klient.

programme.title: Sightings
programme.desc: Ett science fiction-mysterium om en dysfunktionell familj som bor på en ranch i Texas och hotas av en varelse i skogen. For att kunna overleva hotet måste de samtidigt losa sina egna inre konflikter.

programme.title: American Exit
programme.desc: Charlie Bond står infor ett vagskal i livet. Han har nyligen separerat från sin fru och blir ombedd att ta hand om deras son Leo over helgen. Illa tajmat då han just ar i fard med att iscensatta en konstkupp for lite snabba pengar. Leo ar helt ovetandes om planen och bara ser fram emot att får spendera tid med sin efterlangtade pappa. Tatt inpå kommer verkligheten snabbt ikapp Charlie som nu ar i allra hogsta grad en jagad man av skoningslosa torpeder. Hans enda hopp ar att lyckats fly ut ur landet och att få återstalla sin relation till Leo som han vanskott i alla år.

programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: I ett buddhisttempel i Mingdynastins Kina ar det dags for abboten att utse sin eftertradare. Men bland kandidaterna finns det de som framst ar ute efter att stjala den ovarderliga skriften i templets skattkammare. Intriger och allianser uppstår nar personliga ambitioner och andliga stravanden kolliderar.

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: Dragon Lord
programme.desc: Dragon och Bull fordriver tiden mestadels med att glida omkring och jaga tjejer. Speciellt en, som Dragon ar sarskilt fortjust i. Efter ett misslyckat forsok att skicka ett karleksbrev hamnar radarparet ovantat på taket till en kriminellt gangs hogkvarter. Ganget stjal dyrbara artefakter från stadens tempel for att smuggla vidare till giriga vasterlanningar, men Dragon och Bull kanner for forsta gången sin plikt, och bestammer sig for att ta sig an ganget.

programme.title: Saknad i strid (Missing in Action)
programme.desc: Amerikanska soldater hålls fångna i Vietnam — och det ar upp till en man att fora hem dem i denna fartfyllda action/aventyrsfilm med kampsportslegenden Chuck Norris. Efter en djarv flykt från ett krigsfånglager ar overste James Braddock (Norris) på ett uppdrag att lokalisera och radda saknade soldater med hjalp av en tjansteman från utrikesdepartementet (Lenore Kasdorf) och en tidigare armekompis (M. Emmet Walsh). Denna enmansarme ar redo att ta sig in i Vietnam… men kan han ta sig ut igen?

programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape: Episode 2
programme.desc: Three times in the past two decades, the Chiemsee area has experienced "once-in-a-century" floods. Climate, wildlife, and landscape have changed, and it seems this transformation is accelerating. Species living in the flood zones are developing sophisticated survival strategies. Knot ants, for instance, place their queen in the middle and form a raft with their bodies, even conquering new habitats. Flooding is less of a disaster for nature and impacts humans more significantly.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Americas National Parks - Everglades
programme.desc: North America’s National Parks are world famous and their breathtaking landscapes fascinate millions of visitors. This spectacular series will show you what happens beyond the lookouts. Everglades National Park is an American national park that protects the southern twenty percent of the original Everglades in Florida. The park is the largest tropical wilderness in the United States, and the largest wilderness of any kind east of the Mississippi River. An average of one million people visit the park each year. Everglades is the third-largest national park in the contiguous United States after Death Valley and Yellowstone. UNESCO declared the Everglades and Dry Tortugas Biosphere Reserve in...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Americas National Parks - Great Smoky Mountains
programme.desc: Great Smoky Mountains National Park is an American national park in the southeastern United States, with parts in Tennessee and North Carolina. The park straddles the ridgeline of the Great Smoky Mountains, part of the Blue Ridge Mountains, which are a division of the larger Appalachian Mountain chain. The park contains some of the highest mountains in eastern North America, including Clingmans Dome, Mount Guyot, and Mount Le Conte. The border between the two states runs northeast to southwest through the center of the park. The Appalachian Trail passes through the center of the park on its route from Georgia to Maine. With 12.5 million visitors in 2019, the Great Smoky Mountains National...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Americas National Parks - Olympic
programme.desc: Olympic National Park is an American national park located in the State of Washington, on the Olympic Peninsula. The park has four regions: the Pacific coastline, alpine areas, the west side temperate rainforest and the forests of the drier east side. Within the park there are three distinct ecosystems which are subalpine forest and wildflower meadow, temperate forest, and the rugged Pacific coast. President Theodore Roosevelt originally designated Mount Olympus National Monument on 2 March 1909. The monument was redesignated as a national park by Congress and President Franklin Roosevelt on June 29, 1938. In 1976, Olympic National Park was designated by UNESCO as an International...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Americas National Parks - Yosemite
programme.desc: Yosemite National Park is a place of superlatives: with towering cliffs and giant sequoias, home to coyotes, black bears and the most elusive of all: the bobcat. Watch this documentary with ist spectacular shots, aerial views and time-lapse shots and learn some new facts about the biodiversity in one of North Americas most spectacular National Parks.

programme.title: mareTV: Newfoundland - Canadas Eastern Point
programme.desc: In Newfoundland, at the easternmost tip of North America, the landscape is pristine, dramatic, and very sparsely populated. In summer, icebergs occasionally drift along the steep cliffs. When the "Titanic" collided with an iceberg and sank just 300 miles off the coast of Newfoundland in 1912, the last radio messages were picked up in a small wooden hut on the Avalon Peninsula. Today, most Newfoundlanders live on Avalon. There are particularly many seabirds here. In Witless Bay, the newborn puffins are ready for their first descent into the Atlantic. But some stray onto the coastal road, attracted by the lights of the hotels and restaurants. In doing so, they run the risk of being run...

programme.title: Cuba to Go
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Cuba to Go - Episode 1
programme.desc: Ever since the embargo was lifted in the summer of 2015, Cuba’s popularity has been steadily increasing.

programme.desc: Ever since the embargo was lifted in the summer of 2015, Cuba’s popularity has been steadily increasing.

programme.title: Wild Faces of the Andes
programme.desc: The Andes are the biggest mountain range in the world. Peaks of up to 7000 metres in height, do not only offer an imposing view, but also influence the climate by being the drainage and meteorological divide.

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Wild Baltic - Life on the Amber Coast
programme.desc: The first episode of this two-part nature documentary presents the natural beauty of the shifting sand dunes of the Curonian Spit, the romantic beaches of the Latvian Baltic Sea and the island worlds of Estonia. Time and again, this deserted and almost untouched nature fascinates. In the winter, ringed seals give birth to their young on the pack ice. In the spring, Konik wild horse stallions fight fierce battles amongst themselves, while colourful European rollers fly through the dune forests. Lynxes wander through the coastal forests and in the orchid meadows turncoats and hoopoes find more than enough food. On the islands around Saaremaa in Estonia, grey seals hunt for fish. They share...

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Baltic - Enchanted Forests and Moors
programme.desc: The wide, often untouched wilderness of the Baltic hinterland is home to many animals. More than 35 brown bears live in the primeval forests of Alutaguse. In the spring, the Soomaa National Park transforms into a huge lake. Europes widest waterfall is located in Latvia. In the beginning of May, vimba bream follow the course of the River Venta. The hardly 5-centimetre-long fish have to overcome a 4-metre-long rock barrier in order to reach their spawning grounds.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Americas National Parks - Grand Canyon
programme.desc: The Grand Canyon is a steep-sided canyon carved by the Colorado River in Arizona, United States. The Grand Canyon is 277 miles (446 km) long, up to 18 miles (29 km) wide and attains a depth of over a mile (6,093 feet or 1,857 meters). The canyon and adjacent rim are contained within Grand Canyon National Park, the Kaibab National Forest, Grand Canyon–Parashant National Monument, the Hualapai Indian Reservation, the Havasupai Indian Reservation and the Navajo Nation. President Theodore Roosevelt was a major proponent of preservation of the Grand Canyon area and visited it on numerous occasions to hunt and enjoy the scenery.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Americas National Parks - Gates of the Arctic
programme.desc: Gates of the Arctic National Park and Preserve is an American national park that protects portions of the Brooks Range in northern Alaska. The park is the northernmost national park in the United States, situated entirely north of the Arctic Circle. The park is the second largest in the US, slightly larger in area than Belgium. Gates of the Arctic was initially designated as a national monument on December 1, 1978, before being redesignated as a national park and preserve upon passage of the Alaska National Interest Lands Conservation Act in 1980. A large part of the park has additional protection as the Gates of the Arctic Wilderness that adjoins the Noatak Wilderness. They form the...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Americas National Parks - Saguaro
programme.desc: Saguaro National Park is an American national park in Pima County, southeastern Arizona. The 92,000-acre (37,000 ha) park consists of two separate areas—the Tucson Mountain District (TMD) about 10 miles west of the city of Tucson and the Rincon Mountain District (RMD) about 10 miles east of the city—that preserve Sonoran Desert landscapes, fauna, and flora, including the giant saguaro cactus.An inventory of medium and large mammals in the park confirmed the presence of 30 species in Saguaro National Park between 1999 and 2008. Of these, 21 were found in the Tucson Mountain District and 29 in the Rincon Mountain District. A partial list of the parks mammals includes cougars, coyotes,...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Americas National Parks - Yellowstone
programme.desc: Yellowstone National Park is an American national park located in the western United States, largely in the northwest corner of Wyoming and extending into Montana, and Idaho. It was established by the U.S. Congress and signed into law by President Ulysses S. Grant on March 1, 1872. Yellowstone was the first national park in the U.S. and is also widely held to be the first national park in the world. The park is known for its wildlife and its many geothermal features, especially Old Faithful geyser, one of its most popular. While it represents many types of biomes, the subalpine forest is the most abundant. It is part of the South Central Rockies forests ecoregion.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Americas National Parks - Everglades
programme.desc: North America’s National Parks are world famous and their breathtaking landscapes fascinate millions of visitors. This spectacular series will show you what happens beyond the lookouts. Everglades National Park is an American national park that protects the southern twenty percent of the original Everglades in Florida. The park is the largest tropical wilderness in the United States, and the largest wilderness of any kind east of the Mississippi River. An average of one million people visit the park each year. Everglades is the third-largest national park in the contiguous United States after Death Valley and Yellowstone. UNESCO declared the Everglades and Dry Tortugas Biosphere Reserve in...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Americas National Parks - Great Smoky Mountains
programme.desc: Great Smoky Mountains National Park is an American national park in the southeastern United States, with parts in Tennessee and North Carolina. The park straddles the ridgeline of the Great Smoky Mountains, part of the Blue Ridge Mountains, which are a division of the larger Appalachian Mountain chain. The park contains some of the highest mountains in eastern North America, including Clingmans Dome, Mount Guyot, and Mount Le Conte. The border between the two states runs northeast to southwest through the center of the park. The Appalachian Trail passes through the center of the park on its route from Georgia to Maine. With 12.5 million visitors in 2019, the Great Smoky Mountains National...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Americas National Parks - Olympic
programme.desc: Olympic National Park is an American national park located in the State of Washington, on the Olympic Peninsula. The park has four regions: the Pacific coastline, alpine areas, the west side temperate rainforest and the forests of the drier east side. Within the park there are three distinct ecosystems which are subalpine forest and wildflower meadow, temperate forest, and the rugged Pacific coast. President Theodore Roosevelt originally designated Mount Olympus National Monument on 2 March 1909. The monument was redesignated as a national park by Congress and President Franklin Roosevelt on June 29, 1938. In 1976, Olympic National Park was designated by UNESCO as an International...

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Americas National Parks - Yosemite
programme.desc: Yosemite National Park is a place of superlatives: with towering cliffs and giant sequoias, home to coyotes, black bears and the most elusive of all: the bobcat. Watch this documentary with ist spectacular shots, aerial views and time-lapse shots and learn some new facts about the biodiversity in one of North Americas most spectacular National Parks.

programme.title: mareTV: Newfoundland - Canadas Eastern Point
programme.desc: In Newfoundland, at the easternmost tip of North America, the landscape is pristine, dramatic, and very sparsely populated. In summer, icebergs occasionally drift along the steep cliffs. When the "Titanic" collided with an iceberg and sank just 300 miles off the coast of Newfoundland in 1912, the last radio messages were picked up in a small wooden hut on the Avalon Peninsula. Today, most Newfoundlanders live on Avalon. There are particularly many seabirds here. In Witless Bay, the newborn puffins are ready for their first descent into the Atlantic. But some stray onto the coastal road, attracted by the lights of the hotels and restaurants. In doing so, they run the risk of being run...

programme.title: Cuba to Go
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Cuba to Go - Episode 1
programme.desc: Ever since the embargo was lifted in the summer of 2015, Cuba’s popularity has been steadily increasing.

programme.title: Cuba to Go
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Cuba to Go - Episode 2
programme.desc: Ever since the embargo was lifted in the summer of 2015, Cuba’s popularity has been steadily increasing.

programme.title: Wild Faces of the Andes
programme.desc: The Andes are the biggest mountain range in the world. Peaks of up to 7000 metres in height, do not only offer an imposing view, but also influence the climate by being the drainage and meteorological divide.

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Wild Baltic - Life on the Amber Coast
programme.desc: The first episode of this two-part nature documentary presents the natural beauty of the shifting sand dunes of the Curonian Spit, the romantic beaches of the Latvian Baltic Sea and the island worlds of Estonia. Time and again, this deserted and almost untouched nature fascinates. In the winter, ringed seals give birth to their young on the pack ice. In the spring, Konik wild horse stallions fight fierce battles amongst themselves, while colourful European rollers fly through the dune forests. Lynxes wander through the coastal forests and in the orchid meadows turncoats and hoopoes find more than enough food. On the islands around Saaremaa in Estonia, grey seals hunt for fish. They share...

programme.title: Wild Baltic
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Baltic - Enchanted Forests and Moors
programme.desc: The wide, often untouched wilderness of the Baltic hinterland is home to many animals. More than 35 brown bears live in the primeval forests of Alutaguse. In the spring, the Soomaa National Park transforms into a huge lake. Europes widest waterfall is located in Latvia. In the beginning of May, vimba bream follow the course of the River Venta. The hardly 5-centimetre-long fish have to overcome a 4-metre-long rock barrier in order to reach their spawning grounds.

programme.title: North Americas National Parks
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Americas National Parks - Grand Canyon
programme.desc: The Grand Canyon is a steep-sided canyon carved by the Colorado River in Arizona, United States. The Grand Canyon is 277 miles (446 km) long, up to 18 miles (29 km) wide and attains a depth of over a mile (6,093 feet or 1,857 meters). The canyon and adjacent rim are contained within Grand Canyon National Park, the Kaibab National Forest, Grand Canyon–Parashant National Monument, the Hualapai Indian Reservation, the Havasupai Indian Reservation and the Navajo Nation. President Theodore Roosevelt was a major proponent of preservation of the Grand Canyon area and visited it on numerous occasions to hunt and enjoy the scenery.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Of Flying Foxes and Heat Waves
programme.desc: While the Tolga Bat Hospital is looking after endangered flying foxes, researchers are using thermographic cameras to search for flying foxes and koalas. But they can also detect bush and wildfire more quickly.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Of Sea Turtles and Coral Reefs
programme.desc: The Cairns Turtle Rehabilitation Center (CTRC) raises and cares for sick, or injured turtles, while the Schmidt Ocean Institute goes on a diving mission with a high-tech underwater rover. In this way, we learn firsthand about the state of Australias sensitive marine animals natural habitat and what needs to be done to ensure their survival.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Of Wombats and Vaccines
programme.desc: Tasmanias Bonorong Wildlife Sanctuary used to be a traditional wildlife park - now it is an innovative and active wildlife sanctuary and home to the famous Tasmanian Devil, to wombats, and many other native species. But unfortunately, "Tassie Devils" are particularly endangered by the Devil Facial Tumor Disease (DFTD). We accompany the team of young, ambitious scientists on their fight against the disease.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Of Koalas and Drones
programme.desc: Lone Pine Koala Sanctuary was opened in 1927 at a time when Koalas were still being killed on a large scale for the fur trade. Today, hardly anything threatens the natural habitats of these animals as much as the desertification of the forests. We let the drones fly and are there when a new tree is planted.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 wOf Kangaroos and Conservation
programme.desc: Visiting the fenced nature reserve Arid Recovery in southern Australia, we witness the care of an injured kangaroo and follow researchers at the Hidden Vale Wildlife Centre near Brisbane as they train native animals to detect tracks of threatening predators and then move to safety.

programme.title: Wildlife Diaries Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Of Fairy Penguins and GPS Trackers
programme.desc: Australias largest fur seal colony is located on Phillip Island. Night after night, a breathtaking spectacle takes place here: At sunset, countless fairy penguins return from their hunt for fish. In the station near the penguin colony, pioneering scientific research is conducted around the cute animals. We learn how dedicated scientists are trying to secure the future of the fairy penguins with the help of GPS trackers.

programme.title: Symphony of the Seas - Underwater Wonders of Australias Ocean
programme.desc: Our journeys take us all around the world from Patagonia to the USA, from Greenland to South Africa and from Cambodia to Australia and leads us to the most fascinating places where landscapes animals and humans are the main focus of our documentaries. Whether on land or at sea – the last paradises of the world are our destination.

programme.title: Jacques Cousteaus Legacy - Return To The Undersea World
programme.desc: A composition of wildlife footage, archive material and elaborate re-enactments results in a brilliant reconstruction of the life of famed marine biologist and environmental pioneer Jacques Cousteau. On the trail of the most famous oceanographer of the 20th Century, the team spent two years filming original locations on three different continents, in four different oceans. The film charts how Cousteau’s outlook on the environment changed throughout his many decades at sea around the globe. On his personal journey to enlightenment, he changed from a man who killed sharks in hate and thoughtlessly blew up coral reefs, to a radical environmentalist.

programme.title: Red Panda - Worlds Cutest Animal
programme.desc: The Red Panda is undoubtedly one of the most beautiful animals on earth and this is the first ever intimate portrait ever made.

programme.title: New Life
programme.desc: In a land of dangers, plant-eating animals are always at risk, and never more so than at the time of their birth; out on the open they are vulnerable and there are few places to hide. But luckily some are born to run …

programme.title: New Life
programme.desc: Its a water world and life couldnt survive without it. And thanks to it, a mind blowing diversity of creatures thrive beneath the surface. Born to enjoy the riches underwater they must master their bodys adaptations, learn to find food, to escape danger and above all become expert swimmers! Whether its in rivers, on beaches or in the deep ocean, all must overcome the obstacles and fulfil their destiny, all are born to swim! Of all the habitats on earth, the ocean is perhaps the most challenging. Here salt, temperatures, currents and predators can make life difficult; its not an obvious place to want to bring up your babies… But even in these waters generation after generation beats...

programme.title: New Life
programme.desc: Baby animals beguile with their innocent charm. But while some remain harmless, others have a deep-rooted instinct. It may take weeks or months of training to hone their skills. Their landscapes and lifestyles maybe very different, but these babies are born to hunt.

programme.title: Wild Medicine - Animals Superpowers
programme.desc: Nature has many weird creatures to offer and often these animals fascinate us the most. There are ants in Australias outback that use specialised workers as living honey pots. In Africa in the endless Bangweulu wetlands of Zambia the shoebill is on the hunt for fish, a bird that definitely lives up to its name. Finally in the Brazilian rainforests lurk gruesome river monsters in the Amazon abyss that send shivers down the spine of even the most experienced divers. But there are also intense human-animal-relationships like the close bond between a German diver and a dolphin female who explore the Atlantic off the coast of Ireland, or the "easy rider" in California who has taken care of an...

programme.title: Unusual World
programme.desc: The dominance of air has always been in the mind of men, but nature only gave the gift to flight to certain animals. Amongst these, to the insects. Thanks to their wings, the insects have conquered most parts of the planet’s diverse environment. What are the reasons for such an amazing biological success without comparison in the history of the animal world?

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Kinabatangan River: Borneo – Forgotten Paradise
programme.desc: In Sabah, northern Borneo, flows the 560km-long Kinabatangan River. Nowhere else in Sabah are wild animals as easily spotted as along this river: orangutans, elephants, crocodiles, and proboscis monkeys. However, biodiversity is threatened as more rainforest gives way to palm oil plantations. Wildlife ventures into inhabited areas in search of food, leading to conflicts. Locals are fighting to preserve the rainforest and its unique wildlife, demonstrating that conservation and prosperity can coexist even in a modern society.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Pu Mat National Park: Vietnam – Of Bears and Men
programme.desc: The jungle in northern Vietnam is nearly impenetrable, with some areas never touched by humans. The remote rainforests of Pu Mat National Park serve as a refuge for endangered wildlife such as black bears, monkeys, and pangolins. Tuan, a biologist and bear specialist, embarks on an expedition to these untouched regions of the park in search of bears. The most hunted animal here is the pangolin, sought after for its scales believed to have medicinal properties and its meat considered a delicacy. A small Vietnamese conservation organization fights for the survival of this species.

programme.title: Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 Asia - Secret Lives Hidden Places II: Gaoligongshan Park: China – Himalaya’s Gold
programme.desc: The Great Gobi National Park in southwestern Mongolia shelters one of the last populations of wild Bactrian camels, amid its ancient and mysterious desert landscape. With around 800 critically endangered animals, the Gobi remains one of the worlds most sparsely inhabited and inhospitable regions, yet its allure is undeniable, offering a captivating backdrop for encounters with wild camels and stories of people deeply connected to nature.

According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: In the early hours of the morning, Mathilde Croguennec, 18, attending "Teknival" in Brittany, is found at the foot of a tree with her throat cut. An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. programme.title: Candy
programme.desc: Heath Ledger ar den hoppfulla poeten Dan som hals over huvud foralskar sig i konstnaren Candy (Abbie Cornish). Dan ar heroinmissbrukare, men Candy ar fascinerad och dras till honom. Tillsammans beger de sig ut på ostadig mark, sammanbundna av deras vansinniga karlek och glupska sexuella aptit. Med hjalp av universitetsprofessorn Casper (Geoffrey Rush), som kan skaffa dem pengar och få gratis droger, inleder de båda bohemerna en farlig flort med doden.

programme.title: In Tranzit
programme.desc: Baserad på en sann historia. I chockvågorna efter andra varldskriget, under den kalla vintern 1946, skickas av misstag en grupp tyska krigsfångar till ett ryskt kvinnofånglager som styrs av kvinnliga fångvaktare. Fångvaktarna, som forlorat många narstående på grund av Nazisternas brutalitet, mottar de nyanlanda fångarna med stor fientlighet och ser en mojlighet till hamnd...

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax

programme.title: JFK
programme.desc: New Orleans distriktsåklagare Jim Garrison valjer att utreda mordet på president John F. Kennedy i Dallas, Texas, 1963. Det han lar sig får honom att tro att det finns mer till historien an det som allmanheten fick hora.

programme.title: Equals
programme.desc: I en utopisk varld, dar våld och brott i princip ar utplånade via genetisk eliminering av kanslor, lever personer som Nia och Silas ett lugnt, handelselost och dronarlikt liv. De arbetar med att producera informationsmaterial på ett stort kontor och utvaxlar enbart artighetsfraser. Livet ar enkelt, anda till dess att ett rykte borjar florera: en sjukdom som orsakar att manniskor visar kanslor har brutit ut. Om det upptacks av overheten skickas de infekterade ivag, for att aldrig återvanda. Silas misstanker att han bar på sjukdomen och nar det bekraftas, blir han en paria. Trots det dras han till Nia, som också ar infekterad men har lyckats dolja symptomen battre an han sjalv.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: Son of the South
programme.desc: Verklig historia om en KKK-medlems barnbarn som vaxer upp i borjan av 1960-talet. Trots att han fostrats in i hatet intresserar han sig for medborgarrattsrorelsen.

programme.title: K-19: The Widowmaker
programme.desc: 1961 inleder Sovjetunionens forsta karnvapenbarande ubåt på sin jungfruresa i Nordatlanten. Men ubåten fungerar inte optimalt, och når det uppstår fel med karnreaktorn har den katastrofala konsekvenser for besattningen. Tillsammans måste besattningen kampa for att undvika en karnkatastrof som både ar livshotande och kan starta ett nytt varldskrig mellan de två supermakterna.

programme.title: Proxima
programme.desc: Sarah ar en fransk astronaut, och den enda kvinnliga deltagaren i det rymdprogram som forbereder sig infor en ett år lång expedition. Som ensamstående mamma till en åttaåring kanns expeditionen an mer kravande, och med lika delar skuld och mod forsoker hon hitta balans i sin roll som banbrytare och mamma.

programme.title: Jimmy P.
programme.desc: En orolig indianveteran bildar en exceptionell vanskap med en fransk psykoanalytiker nar de forsoker hitta botemedel mot deras lidande.

programme.title: Winged Creatures
programme.desc: På ett ogonblick forandras allt - hur går du vidare nar ditt liv slås i spillror? Det ar tidig morgon i Los Angeles, en psykopat skjuter besinningslost ihjal ett antal oskyldiga manniskor på en frukostservering... Hur reagerar de som overlever eller de anhoriga till de som mordats av en slump?

programme.title: Black Coal, Thin Ice
programme.desc: På en kolfabrik liksom vid en soptipp, i olika andar av provinsen Heilongjian, påtraffas delar från samma kropp. En man har styckats och spridits ut, på ett avstånd for stort for en ensam garningsman. Zhang Zili (spelad av Liao Fan, som belonades for basta skådespelarinsats i Berlin) åtar sig fallet, men under ett misslyckat ingripande blir två av hans kollegor skjutna och Zhang tvingas lamna sin tjanst. Fem år senare blir Zhang uppsokt av sin forne kollega. Ett dubbelmord, identiskt med det som agde rum 1999, har skett och Zhang får chansen till återupprattelse.

programme.title: The Greatest
programme.desc: Allen och Grace Brewer har forlorat sin aldsta son i en bilolycka, nar det plotsligt ringerpå dorren. Utanfor står Rose. Hon sager att hon kande deras son. Och att hon vantar hans barn. Forst får det familjen att falla isar ytterligare. Men kanske kan avenden svåraste olycka leda till ny lycka?

programme.title: Danny Collins
programme.desc: Al Pacino spelar 1970-talsrockaren Danny Collins som fortfarande lever hårt for att do ung. Nar hans manager hittar ett brev som John Lennon 40 år tidigare skrev till Danny, ett brev som han aldrig har last, så bestammer han sig for att byta kurs. Han ger sig ut på en gripande resa for att hitta tillbaka till sin familj, hitta den sanna karleken och påborja nasta akt i livet. Det fantastiska soundtracket innehåller låtar av John Lennon.

programme.title: Runaway Jury
programme.desc: Från mastaren John Grisham kommer en thriller med Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, John Cusack och Rachel Weisz. En jury-fixare spelar ett dodligt katt-och-råtta-spel med en jurymedlem och en mystisk framling som båda erbjuder att "leverera" domen till hogstbjudande. Snart står både liv och miljoner på spel i en pulshojare full av ovantade vandningar.

programme.title: Birdman
programme.desc: I den omtalade och kritikerhyllade svarta komedin BIRDMAN eller The Unexpected Virtue of Ignorance ser vi Michael Keaton i huvudrollen som en skådespelare, mest kand for att ha spelat den ikoniska superhjalten Birdman. Han ska nu regissera en teateruppforestallning på Broadway och vi får folja honom under de hektiska dagarna innan den stora premiarkvallen. Samtidigt som han slåss mot sina inre demoner och sitt stora ego så forsoker han lappa ihop både familj och karriar. For regi står Alejandro G. Iñárritu (BABEL, ÄLSKADE HUNDAR) och i ovriga roller ser vi bl.a. Zach Galifianakis, Edward Norton, Emma Stone, Naomi Watts.

I avskedsgåva får han ett par smartglasogon, som vacker anvandarens storsta drommar till liv. Nar Felix frus karriar tar fart och dottern borjar bli sjalvstandig inser Felix hur ensam han kanner sig. For att fly den plågsamma ensamheten fordjupar Felix sig allt mer i sina smartglasogons varld, vilket påfrestar Felix relation till familjen ytterligare.

programme.title: Hot Mess
programme.desc: Wardens gear up for the last week of the season. The pressure is on, putting the Wardens right in the middle of a Hot Mess.

programme.title: The Philippines
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 The Travel Bug S1 - "The Philippines"
programme.desc: The Philippines is a beautiful nation. The archipelago contains countless islands, sandy beaches and smiling faces. Best of all it is a destination where one day you can relax in a luxury resort, then the next you can get dirty in a street market.

programme.title: New South Wales, Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 The Travel Bug S1 - "New South Wales, Australia"
programme.desc: Starting in Sydney, we travel over the Harbour Bridge and dine with koalas, before heading into the Blue Mountains and out to the far west to the ancient landscape of Mungo National Park. This desert landscape has a fascinating story.

programme.title: Divide and Conquer
programme.sub-title: S02 : E09 Dropped: Project Alaska S2 - "Divide and Conquer"
programme.desc: Chris needs to make this happen. With willows to high to attempt a shot from the current location, Chris frantically pushes and closes the distance to 300 yards.

programme.title: Weathered and Worn
programme.sub-title: S02 : E10 Dropped: Project Alaska S2 - "Weathered and Worn"
programme.desc: The brothers devise a plan and advance toward the bull. Mid-stalk, the bull rises and approaches them, turning away just before Casey can line up the scope behind its shoulder.

programme.title: Return Home
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 The Trail S1 - "Return Home"
programme.desc: Laramy and 7 say goodbye to their final camp and head home.

programme.title: Seperation Anxiety
programme.desc: Alaskan weather clears for Chris and Kaid to hunt food, while Casey and R.L. set up camp before moose season. Its their first time being Dropped separately, requiring adjustment.

programme.title: Predators Prowl
programme.desc: Chris and Kaid ready their rafts while Casey and R.L. begin searching for black bears and moose. Chris and Kaid spot a predator heading toward camp.

programme.title: Volcanic Kingfish
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Man Eats Wild S1 - "Volcanic Kingfish"
programme.desc: Mario hooks up with old friend and current world record holder for kingfish Rick Pollock. They fish the coast of New Zealand just off a live Volcano, then tragedy strikes. After the Volcano erupts Mario prepares an amazing ceviche dish.

programme.title: FMX Nomads
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 FMX Nomads S1 - "FMX Nomads"
programme.desc: Join Dan Whitby, Samson Eaton and Arran Powley for a day in the life of globetrotting freestyle motocross team, Bolddog.

programme.title: Meet Island Air
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Alaskas Ultimate Bush Pilots S1 - "Meet Island Air"
programme.desc: Veteran bush pilot Bob Stanford risks everything to save hunters struggling to stay alive in a remote area of Kodiak.

programme.title: Fight or Flight
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Alaskas Ultimate Bush Pilots S1 - "Fight or Flight"
programme.desc: While on a routine sightseeing flight, a massive storm has the pilots fighting to keep control of the craft and keep their passengers safe.

programme.title: Deadmans Survival
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Alaskas Ultimate Bush Pilots S1 - "Deadmans Survival"
programme.desc: Island Air battles time and elements, to rescue a group trapped in Deadmans Bay.

programme.title: The Broads
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Hunting Fish S1 - "The Broads"
programme.desc: Thom hunt is challenged to hunt the mighty Pike in the Uk’s Norfolk Broads.

programme.title: Extremadura
programme.desc: Thom hunt is challenged to hunt a record-breaking Barbel in the Spain’s striking Extremadura.

programme.title: UK
programme.desc: Thom hunt challenges himself to locate and catch four UK species in one week.

programme.title: Tippets and Leaders
programme.sub-title: S01 : E07 Buccaneers and Bones S1 - "Tippets and Leaders"
programme.desc: The teams goal of landing and tagging a mature tarpon is fulfilled, as one of the anglers lands a 60lbs silver king. Michael Keaton and Yvon Choulnard spend time wading throught the flats together and we look back on the week spend in Belize.

programme.title: Day Two Pt. 1
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Madfin Shark Series S1 - "Day Two Pt. 1"
programme.desc: Day two of the Madfin Shark Series begins, as its becoming clearer which of our four 2-man teams will have to do whatever it takes to not be in last place and being eliminated. Hurricane Hole Marina in Key West sees the sharks finding captains idle.

programme.title: Day Two Pt.2
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Madfin Shark Series S1 - "Day Two Pt.2"
programme.desc: Day two and the battle continues on the Madfin Shark Series. Four of our 2-man teams are catching and releasing the biggest and most dangerous sharks they can for the most points they can accrue. After today, one team will be sent home and eliminated.

programme.title: Day Three Pt. 1
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Madfin Shark Series S1 - "Day Three Pt. 1"
programme.desc: Its the third and final day of competition for the remaining 3 teams in this intense shark tournament. See how the first half of the day turns out.

programme.title: Far North Bluewater Mission
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 South Seas Spearo S2 - "Far North Bluewater Mission"
programme.desc: 60 nautical miles + 200kg of Burley divided by 3 keen spearos = mayhem. The team go wide this week, overnighting aboard The Orca in 1000m of water in the Far North, in an attempt to create a 24-hour trail capable of attracting in who knows what!

programme.title: Hardcore Hapuka
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 South Seas Spearo S2 - "Hardcore Hapuka"
programme.desc: We return to Fiordland in the hope of going one step better in slotting a hapuka on a spear, but the presence of Bluefin Tuna off the coast, and Wapiti Bulls on the slip faces proves a tempting distraction from the task at hand!

programme.title: Pitt Island Expedition
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 South Seas Spearo S2 - "Pitt Island Expedition"
programme.desc: Following a ridiculous sequence of events in Fiordland, the team saddle up and head for the hapuka haven of the Chatham Islands, where they spend a few days diving the spectacular and remote Pitt Island.

programme.title: ATV Accidents
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Survival Science S1 - "ATV Accidents"
programme.desc: ATVs have allowed us to penetrate the wilderness like never before. But they’ve also made the backcountry a bit more dangerous. Laura and Nick rig up some dramatic, high-speed tests to see how accidents happen and what you can do to protect yourself.

programme.title: Episode 4
programme.desc: The team battles high winds in the heli to save a snowmobiler with a busted femur.

programme.title: Episode 5
programme.desc: Unprecedented three rescues in under twelve hours.

programme.title: Episode 6
programme.desc: Jamie puts his trust in new explosives technology.

programme.title: The Journal
programme.sub-title: S02 : E07 Fight to Survive S2 - "The Journal"
programme.desc: Pastor Mike Turner is on a solo hike across the continental divide in the unforgiving Wind Rivers Range of Wyoming, when he becomes hopelessly trapped under a boulder. He chronicles his grueling 11 day fight to survive in his own journal.

programme.title: Tree Stand Fall
programme.sub-title: S02 : E08 Fight to Survive S2 - "Tree Stand Fall"
programme.desc: Deer hunter Nathan Holcomb plummets from his tree stand. Every hunters’ worst nightmare becomes Nathan’s reality. With a broken back paralyzing him, Nathan must crawl out on his own to find help.

programme.title: Adrift Pt. 1
programme.sub-title: S02 : E09 Fight to Survive S2 - "Adrift Pt. 1"
programme.desc: In what is regarded as one of greatest survival stories of the 20th Century, sailor Steven Callahan finds himself alone and adrift in a life raft after his boat, the Napoleon Solo, sinks in the mid Atlantic.

programme.title: Nicosia
programme.desc: Josh is in Cyprus for a local exploring adventure across the island on a roadtrip from Nicosia to an abandoned amusement park, an asbestos mine and a shipwreck.

programme.title: New Orleans
programme.sub-title: S02 : E12 Epic Exploring S2 - "New Orleans"
programme.desc: Cody is with Lexi Limitless in the ‘Big Easy’ to explore New Orleans, visiting an abandoned Charity Hospital before meeting Brutus, the giant alligator.

programme.title: Yerevan
programme.desc: Josh goes local exploring in Armenia and its capital Yerevan, visiting some amazing abandoned Soviet buildings, a knitting factory and a luxurious hotel.

programme.title: Madagascar
programme.desc: A Canadian MTB adventurer explores Madagascar and shows the behind the scenes processes of making a film.

programme.title: Norway
programme.desc: An Irish MTB pro rider discovers and rides the most amazing trails that Norway has to offer from the mountains to the ocean.

programme.title: Alaska
programme.desc: We follow one of the best MTB riders and trail-builders on the planet during a trip in Alaska, one of the most remote and wild places in the world.

programme.title: Meet the Smiths
programme.sub-title: S04 : E04 Hollywood Weapons: Fact or Fiction? S4 - "Meet the Smiths"
programme.desc: Terry finally gets to compare himself to Brad Pitt!! Terry and Larry test 3 scenes from action film Mr. and Mrs. Smith. Can a refrigerator or elevator door protect our heroes? Also, can you ignite a gas line with just a bullet? Larry may not look as stunning as Angelina Jolie, but he will help Terry find out the answers.

programme.title: Nightmare on Hollywood Weapons
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 Hollywood Weapons: Fact or Fiction? S4 - "Nightmare on Hollywood Weapons"
programme.desc: Terry and Larry get to test several scenes from Horror films! Terry wants to find out what is the best way to kill a Zombie, just in case he ever ends up in a Zombie Apocalypse, and they will test a scene from the horror classic, Freddie vs. Jason!

programme.title: All for One!
programme.sub-title: S04 : E06 Hollywood Weapons: Fact or Fiction? S4 - "All for One!"
programme.desc: Terry travels back in time to see if he can make it as a Three Musketeer! Can he throw his sword and kill the enemy? Can the cross that he wears around his neck stop a bullet? Can a lead ball ignite from a black powder ignite a carriage full of black powder and brandy? Terry enlists the help of his companions to find out!

programme.title: Croatia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Running the World S1 - "Croatia"
programme.desc: Max and Benj Cave travel to Croatia to meet up with local parkour experts and undertake an epic run in an abandoned aluminium factory.

programme.title: Santorini
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Running the World S1 - "Santorini"
programme.desc: A challenge to race each other and a labyrinth of narrow streets and hidden passages to navigate will make this one of the trickiest challenges.

programme.title: Best of ep. 1 to 5
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Running the World S1 - "Best of ep. 1 to 5"
programme.desc: Parkour athletes Max and Benj Cave look back over their travels so far and discuss the best places for practising parkour.

programme.desc: Supercar Blondie goes to Hollywood arriving in a million dollar V12 Ferrari. In the ‘City of Angels’ Alex is brought into contact with the Brotherhood of Racing, a community of drivers looking to create safe racing conditions for amateurs.

programme.title: Houston
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Car Crews with Supercar Blondie S1 - "Houston"
programme.desc: Given special access to a 2 million dollar exclusive McClaren Senna, Supercar Blondie digs under the surface to uncover gang feuds in the SLAB (Slow, Low and Bangin’) community and meets up with legendary hip hop artists Slim Thug and Paul Wall.

programme.desc: Eric Hanson heads to British Columbia’s beautiful Sunshine Coast, to explore the 112-mile long Sunshine Coast Trail and to test his nerves at the Coast Gravity Downhill Mountain Bike Park.

programme.title: The Gift of Faith
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 Kindness Diaries S2 - "The Gift of Faith"

programme.title: Vanuatu
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 The Travel Bug S2 - "Vanuatu"
programme.desc: Vanuatu has countless pretty and unspoiled beaches, with palm trees overhanging the water and islands where rainforests cover the landscape. But the strongest asset of this Pacific paradise is

programme.title: Korea
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 The Travel Bug S2 - "Korea"
programme.desc: Korea is a fascinating and complex nation. It’s a place where ancient Confucianism is juxtaposed with an insatiable appetite for technology. We start at the heart of this thriving nation, Seoul.

programme.title: The Record
programme.sub-title: S02 : E06 The Flying Kestrel S2 - "The Record"
programme.desc: Driver Jon Webster is strapped in and ready to push the Flying Kestrel to its limits.The Kestrel team must overcome multiple problems on the day to stand any chance of topping the time sheets and can Jon keep the kestrel on track and break the record

programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Travel Quest S1 - "North Pole"
programme.desc: The crew takes an icebreaker to the North Pole just in time to make a satellite phone call to wish Bills mother a happy birthday (she is so shocked she doesnt recognize him). We also track and film the biggest predators on earth…polar bears.

programme.title: Rwanda…Gorillas
programme.desc: Bill tracks through never ending mud, heavy vegetation and steep mountains, to come face-to-face with our mighty cousins. He also traces the life, and finds the remnants, of the camp of one of his idols - Diane Fossey.

programme.title: Botswana
programme.desc: Botswana is a wildlife lover’s dream with massive herds of elephants, immense pods of hippos and some of the largest prides of lions anywhere. It’s also the home of Victoria Falls…the largest falls in the world.

programme.title: Donsol, Philippines
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Beyond The Beaten Path S1 - "Donsol, Philippines"
programme.desc: Disaster and triumph set this show apart. The brothers start out with a near death boat disaster in the southern Philippine Sea but bounce back and end up attaining their goal of reaching Donsol village, the whale shark capitol of the world.

programme.title: The Journey Begins
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Extreme Iceland S1 - "The Journey Begins"
programme.desc: Mike kickstarts his trip by leaving Bermuda and heading to Iceland via Boston in the USA, where delivery issues threaten to stop his adventure before it even begins.

programme.sub-title: S02 : E08 Travel Quest S2 - "Polar Bears"
programme.desc: There is one place in the world where the mighty polar bear—largest carnivore on earth—can be found in large numbers during a very specific time of the year…Churchill Manitoba, Canada.

programme.title: Namibia
programme.desc: Bill has a dual quest—the first to visit one of the greatest deserts in the world and find out how the creatures and plants survive. The other is a bit unorthodox and maybe unbelievable – he’s going to seek, and hopefully find, the mythical unicorn.

programme.title: Long Day
programme.desc: When elk start to migrate the days get long. Wardens keep an eye on the herd and find that at night it really gets weird.

programme.title: Bad Decisions
programme.desc: Ethical hunters make the right decisions every day. This week Wardens find themselves confronted with Bad Decisions.

programme.title: Fly By
programme.desc: Wardens set up a check station in Region 5. When the hunters decide to run it the chase is on.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Alaskas Ultimate Bush Pilots S1 - "Desperate Times"
programme.desc: Island Air drops off a group of desperate hunters in the heart of the bush as a deep freeze hits Kodiak.

programme.title: Risky Business
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Alaskas Ultimate Bush Pilots S1 - "Risky Business"
programme.desc: Pilot Peter Rosendahl combats gale force wind and choppy seas while taxing a group of hunters to a floating lodge.

programme.title: Training Day
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Alaskas Ultimate Bush Pilots S1 - "Training Day"
programme.desc: New pilots are put to the test to see if they have what it takes to fly for Island Air.

programme.title: Into The High Lonesome
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Trail S1 - "Into The High Lonesome"

programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 The Trail S1 - "Camp Otis"
programme.desc: Life at Camp Otis. Laramy finds success fishing and foraging, and spends his time taking care of 7 and doing camp chores.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Roads End S1 - "San Juan to Laguna Brava"
programme.desc: In this episode Rob and Dave put the drama of Rob’s broken clutch behind them and go full steam ahead from San Juan to Laguna Brava.

programme.title: Salt Flats
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Roads End S1 - "Salt Flats"
programme.desc: Rob and Dave are continuing on through the stunning scenery of Laguna Brava towards Corona del Inca. That’s not all they’ve got in store though.

programme.title: Two Dish Battle
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 Cooks on Fire S2 - "Two Dish Battle"
programme.desc: Six teams meet host Ganesh Raj and BBQ experts Jared Macdonald and Jess Pryles in Waiamuku to begin the ultimate barbecue battle. They are challenged to make two dishes that showcase their barbecue skills: one low ‘n slow and one hot ‘n fast.

programme.title: From Ohrigstad to Pilgrims Rest
programme.sub-title: S01 : E15 The Armchair Adventurer S1 - "From Ohrigstad to Pilgrims Rest"
programme.desc: From the Echo Caves of South Africa to the historical Pilgrims Rest, Xander begins to feel at home again in the location where he grew up.

programme.title: Winelands of the Cape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E16 The Armchair Adventurer S1 - "Winelands of the Cape"
programme.desc: While Xander and his team enjoy good food and wine at the family owned Spier Wine Farm, Adam spends his day making cider and looking through his family’s belongings.

programme.title: From Grabouw to Botriver
programme.sub-title: S01 : E17 The Armchair Adventurer S1 - "From Grabouw to Botriver"
programme.desc: A wine farm surrounded by mountains, a day of hiking and picnics, and delectable food paired with premium wine is on the itinerary for Xander and his team as they make their way from Grabouw to Botrivier.

programme.title: Cloudy Days
programme.desc: On day two of the hunting season, Chris and Kaid explore downstream for a better location and fish. Meanwhile, Casey and R.L. savor salmon for protein. Alaska is pounded by massive storm clouds.

programme.title: Soaked Spirits
programme.desc: R.L. opens up to Casey about the trials that led him to realize the importance of Be Alive. Chris and Kaid are holed up in the tent at the mercy of the Alaskan weather. Casey and R.L. find some food.

programme.title: Bearing Down
programme.desc: While enjoying some supper, Casey spots a bear browsing the hillside. He and R.L. make a mad dash in the rain to attempt to get within range. Chris is growing tired of being stuck in the tent.

programme.title: Adrift Pt. 2
programme.sub-title: S02 : E10 Fight to Survive S2 - "Adrift Pt. 2"
programme.desc: Facing starvation, dehydration and predators from the deep, sailor Steven Callahan fights to survive not only the physical hardships, but also the mental and emotional strain of being adrift and alone in a disintegrating life raft.

programme.title: Nightmare Canyon - Part 1
programme.sub-title: S03 : E01 Fight to Survive S3 - "Nightmare Canyon - Part 1"
programme.desc: Justin and Jeremy Harris’ weekend decent into a remote Utah canyon becomes a survival nightmare when Justin severely breaks his leg. As night fast approaches and temperatures drop below freezing, how will these two brothers survive?

programme.title: Nightmare Canyon - Part 2
programme.sub-title: S03 : E02 Fight to Survive S3 - "Nightmare Canyon - Part 2"
programme.desc: After Justin Harris severely breaks his leg deep in a remote, Utah canyon, it ‘s up to his brother Jeremy to climb out for help. Clawing his way through icy pools of water and up rock faces, pushes Jeremy to his limit.

programme.title: Day 6
programme.desc: After exploring Peru, Jalou has to get over her fear when she goes white water kayaking. In Thailand, Kevin is feeling the pressure.

programme.title: Day 7
programme.desc: After a week, Kevin and Jalou find themselves in the same country again: Canada. They travel from Vancouver to Whistler for the final challenge.

programme.title: The Pagoda
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Geared Up S1 - "The Pagoda"
programme.desc: The team does a restoration modification of a 1964 Mercedes Benz 230 SL, adding custom made wheels and a modern engine.

programme.title: Jaisalmer: India’s Hidden Gem
programme.sub-title: S02 : E04 Journeys in India S2 - "Jaisalmer: India’s Hidden Gem"
programme.desc: Every major country has a destination that is incredible but not well known to outsiders—Jaisalmer is such a place. Once a major stop along the silk road, this living museum and surrounding countryside has something for everyone.

programme.title: Gujarat: Land of Extremes
programme.sub-title: S02 : E05 Journeys in India S2 - "Gujarat: Land of Extremes"
programme.desc: The people and wildlife of the western state of Gujarat have found ways to survive in an inhospitable environment. Unique big game exists side-by-side with some of the most talented and unique craftsman in the world.

programme.title: Ibiza
programme.desc: DJ-producer Carly Foxx travels to the clubbing capital of the world to inspire her music track and discovers Ibiza’s alternative spiritual side.

programme.title: Europe

programme.title: Cape Town
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 A Simple Path S1 - "Cape Town"

programme.title: Johannesburg
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 A Simple Path S1 - "Johannesburg"
programme.desc: Empowered in Jozi the city of gold South Africa with the kids from Skateistan, leftfield artists and photographers, streetside Kotas, volcano sessions, Slappy screen printing, a backyard ramp and skating through an art gallery.

programme.title: Day 5
programme.desc: In the Chinese desert, Kevin finds out that desert racing is difficult. While in Bolivia, Jalou wants to prove to her brother that women can be better drivers.

programme.title: Quebec
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Travels with Darley S1 - "Quebec"

programme.title: Låt de doda vila

Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: Epic Movie
programme.desc: Dina favoriter från de basta Hollywoodfilmerna blir extremt roligt parodierade i denna galna komedi! Fyra foraldralosa och problemfyllda karaktarer (från fyra kanda filmer) blir fångna i en bisarr chokladfabrik. De lyckas så småningom fly till en magisk varld full med låtsas-snooch riktiga trollerier...

programme.title: Mama Weed
programme.desc: Nar en underbetald polistolk under ett tillslag upptacker att en av de involverade ar en person i hennes narhet tar hon ett livsavgorande beslut. Hon lyckas beslagta den massiva mangden hasch både polisen och den undre varlden vill åt, och med hennes erfarenheter i faltet och polisens resurser borjar hon sin egna kriminella verksamhet och sadlar om till knarklangare.

programme.title: A Haunted House
programme.desc: I denna skandalosa parodi på Paranormal Activity-filmerna hemsoks ett ungt par som precis flyttat in i sitt dromhem. Kort efter inflyttning upptacker de att de inte langre ar ensamma. Men det ar inte huset som ar hemsokt, det ar Malcolms flickvan. Malcolm hyr in allt från praster till Ghostbusters så att denna demon inte ska få forstora hans forhållande ... eller, annu viktigare, hans sexliv.

programme.title: The Happytime Murders
programme.desc: I en varld dar "puppets" lever bland manniskor, men inte riktigt har uppnåt samma status, jobbar detektiv Phil (spelad av Bill Barretta). Han återforenas med sin forna partner, detektiv Connie Edwards (Melissa McCarthy) for att hitta den som mordade detektiv Phils bror och som nu ar ute efter flera ur casten till 80-talets succe-TV-serie The Happytime Gang. Phils gamla tjej (spelad av Elisabeth Banks) har utsatts for hot och ar nasta tilltankta offer. Snart pekar misstankarna mot Phil sjalv. Han sticker och måste nu ensam forsoka losa The happytime murders.

programme.title: Peace, Love and Misunderstanding
programme.desc: En komedi om en overspand New York advokat (Oscarsnominerade® Catherine Keener) som tar med sig sina två pigga tonåringar till hennes hippie mors (Oscarsbelonade® Jane Fonda) hus på landet for en familjesemester. Det var tankt att bli en avkopplande helgutflykt men som snabbt forvandlas till en sommar fylld med aventyr, romantik, musik, familjehemligheter och om att hitta sig sjalv.

programme.title: Meet Bill
programme.desc: Mot Bill - en akta toffelhjalte! Han jobbar dygnet runt på sin svarfars bank och blir svårt utnyttjad av sin fru som avskyr att tvingas forklara sin så kallade "vanskap" med den tvålfagre Chip, en manlig lokaltv-personlighet. En dag råkar han på Lucy, en sot butiksexpedit for en underkladesaffar och livet tycks antligen ta en positiv vandning. Tillsammans tar de sig an att bygga upp Bills dåliga sjalvfortroende!

programme.title: Three Day Millionaire
programme.desc: En skranig komedi om ett gang unga fiskare från Grimsbys regndrankta hamn i norra England, som måste genomfora sitt livs kupp for att radda staden. Glom Oceans 11, och gor er redo for Grimsbys 4.

programme.title: 36 Husbands
programme.desc: 36 Husbands ar en mystisk, musikalisk, Kung Fu-spionkomedi med tre maktiga kvinnor – och ett gang akta man. Toppspionen och Kung Fu-mastaren Krista har speciella krafter och hon anvander dem for att få marschen mot ett tredje varldskrig att gå långsammare.

Tillsammans med sin cellkamrat Max bestammer han sig for att iscensatta en spektakular bankkupp. Och sen moter han Julie, en alldeles bedårande teaterdiva, vilket leder till en hel del ovantade problem.

programme.desc: Nar Norval får ett ovantat brev från sin frånvarande far, reser han till faderns ensligt belagna hus vid havet. Men mycket snart marker han att något kanns valdigt konstigt, och istallet for en efterlangtad familjeåtertraff ar han istallet fast i en helvetisk mardrom.

programme.title: 68 Kill
programme.desc: Ett fullodigt romantiskt aventyr om kvinnligt, manligt och stolden av 68 000 dollar från den prisbelonte regissoren Trent Haaga. Chip ar en vanlig enkel kille och hans Liza ar en helt suveran flickvan. Visst drygar hon ut parets inkomster med hjalp av en sugardaddy, men alla relationer ar lite knepiga på sitt satt. Nar hon foreslår att de ska sno en massa stålar från hennes sliskige valgorare borjar Chip se en sida av Liza som han inte visste fanns... Nu har han en pistol i handen, en tjej i bagageutrymmet och mindre an 24 timmar på sig att komma på hur han ska ta sig ur den har roran.

The first sound film for Hollywood heavyweight Clark Gable, The Painted Desert finds Boyd and Gable at odds over the affections of a cowboys beautiful daughter (Helen Twelvetrees).

programme.desc: Sheriff Hopalong Cassidy triumphs again in this lighthearted western romp from Harry Sherman Productions. Good ol Hoppy (William Boyd) has to leave his beloved Texas to track down some bad guys in Oklahoma. You can bet that the action and suspense will follow Hopalong wherever he goes. Also, look for a number of familiar faces in the ast, including TVs future Superman George Reeves, notorious Hollywood heavy Victor Jory, and in his first credited role, Robert Mitchum! In fact, Mitchum would appear in more of Hoppys adventures before branching out on his own and becoming one of Hollywoods greatest stars. Also featuring Jan Christy, Forbes Murray, Byron Foulger, Earle Hodgins, and Roy...

programme.title: The Drifter
programme.desc: He only wants to return home to his cabin in the woods, but the man known as The Drifter finds himself involved with a murder! Director William A. OConnor, whose career included everything from drug scare movies to the early films of John Wayne, gives us a dramatic and savage tale of family secrets. With excellent performances by William Farnum and Noah Beery, The Drifter is an early talkie that still pulsates with the angst and melodrama of the silent era...

programme.title: Fighting Fury
programme.desc: A THRILLING TALE OF REVENGE AND REDEMPTION! Based on the story Triple Cross for Danger by the widely lauded Western author Walter J. Coburn, Fighting Fury is a thrilling take on the Western revenge drama. Portraying both a father and his son, star of silent and sound cowboy adventure films, Jack Hoxie (Trouble Busters, Law and Lawless) exudes the classic American rustic charm that still defines the genre. The film spins the yarn of Clay Hill Jr. (Hoxie), a Spanish-American boy raised by a Mexican servant who vows bloody vengeance on three malicious ranchers after they murder his parents and turn his life upside down. Featuring fine supporting performances from genre heavies Helen Holmes,...

Look for the usual cast of characters from Republic Pictures, including Smiley Burnette (as the irresistible Frog Millhouse!). Songs include Take Me Back To My Boots and Saddle, and Ridin the Range.

For trivia buffs: Smiley Burnette joined Roy because Gene Autry, the actor for whom he usually served as a sidekick, had joined the service!

Directed by Ray Taylor; starring Smith Ballew, Gehrig, Evelyn Knapp. Talk about stunt casting! Gehrig was a New York Yankees star who was nearing the end of his career, but one of the biggest sports stars in the country. In the movie he plays a variation of himself, as Lou Gehrig, a retired baseball player who takes up ranching. Lou expects to relax on his ranch but quickly joins other ranchers in a fight to protect their properties.

With the help of his pals California Carson and Jimmy Rogers, he sets out to expose the real culprits and clear Tims name. The usual cast is here, including William Boyd as Hoppy, plus Andy Clyde, Jimmy Rogers, and in one of his earliest roles, Robert Mitchum.

Also, be on the lookout for the beautiful Christine McIntyre, who would go on to appear in several of the Three Stooges shorts for Colombia Pictures.

Bob Steele, one of the busiest stars in movie history (everything from the silent era to Republic Pictures to working with Clint Eastwood in Hang Em High) is here as Tom Shaw, the target of a bad mans desperation and hate. Steele appeared in more than 240 movies and television shows, but was never more impressive than in The Red Rope!

This old-fashioned shoot-em-up was directed by William Witney, who would go on to direct many of televisions top western sagas, including Bonanza, Wagon Train, and The Wild, Wild West.
